OL,3,CRecycling plant fined after exposing
OL,4,Cworkers to cancer-causing dust
OL,6,FThe company provided a detailed
OL,7,Fresponse, and it was accepted that
OL,8,Fexposures to the surrounding area was
OL,9,Fin large part due to four storms in
OL,10,Fquick succession.
OL,12,FHowever, the HSE investigation found
OL,13,Fthat the control of wood dust to
OL,14,Fprotect employees working on and
OL,15,Faround the site was not adequate and
OL,16,Ffell short of the expected benchmark.
OL,18,FThe company failed to design and
OL,19,Foperate processes and activities to
OL,20,Fminimise emission, release and spread
OL,21,Fof wood dust.
